\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57b2177f134425524650603dac681dad24efba9","tid":308463,"uid":37005,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多謝各位巴絲<br />\n冇錯我係垃圾係 On9仔<br />\n我以前都接受唔到任何出軌行為<br />\n但係感情事係咪可以冇時冇刻保持理性, 保持你道德標準<br />\n我相信大把人都會某程度上做錯過<br />\n但我好多謝各位屌醒我 要繼續屌亦係你地自由<br />\n特別多謝提醒我做人個位巴打<br />\n我已同女神講清楚<br />\n答返爸打問題 我冇屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢當年係錯過就係錯過左</blockquote><br />\n自己做錯嘢就拉埋其他人落水<br />\n你真係唔死都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又係嗰啲出軌就係犯咗天下間男人都會犯嘅錯一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我想講對女友對感情忠誠嘅好男人仲有好多"},{"pid":"c45f49cbbbaa53b28bfa8fa9b082d5a8bd62ebd9","tid":308463,"uid":123251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:22:44.000Z","msg":"珍惜曖昧過嘅回憶 你一齊只會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17c58096c3172c37f82fd275d1c1dabce685cb9","tid":308463,"uid":10621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T03:25:23.000Z","msg":"認真答樓主 其實你心入面已經有答案啦 你只係怕做衰人姐 偽善撚一名"},{"pid":"25d79347e032f1908ce3b89e41635ac228411798","tid":308463,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:02:56.000Z","msg":"其實你揀邊一個都會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為你揀左一個，永遠唔會知揀另一個係點"},{"pid":"23c37ca1d34c0d92819d169a1394519121f569ae","tid":308463,"uid":90654,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"坦白7年咩都變啦，重係你當初鍾意果個？明知你拍左咁耐，都同你一齊，小心下個月同你講大肚啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不過啦，點睇你都唔會醒嫁啦，你都係想我地同你講同你女神一齊嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3895e91aad32b685aacdee934a2c0412adf14f8b","tid":308463,"uid":33125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:25:28.000Z","msg":"其實所謂最愛 永遠係得唔到個個先叫最愛<br />\n因為得唔到既 人係犯賤會想要 <br />\n<br />\n到呢個所謂最愛到左手，自然第二個會變做你既至愛 所以收手啦"},{"pid":"097d22a477bbce6e5049e8d99a50b1b9d9f302fc","tid":308463,"uid":57168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:41:08.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"60b0852958e87db9054ca6ce86b04cebab3ab99b","tid":308463,"uid":80816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T21:32:35.000Z","msg":"明知你有拍拖都痴埋去既女仔好極有限<br />\n你覺得佢好係因為你未擁有過<br />\n什麼一生中最愛？<br />\n如果你唔要七年個個 你之後一定會後悔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n狗男女正垃圾 <br />\n明知自己有女朋友就檢點啲啦<br />\n明知人地有拍拖仲痴埋去真係仆街 <br />\n祝樓主無限戴<span style=\"color: green;\">帽</span>或者他朝幫人養仔<br />\n你女朋友最寶貴既時間比哂你 你竟然咁對佢"},{"pid":"3f70149ee2676e395cd1c86a84cf0edb4a821f34","tid":308463,"uid":86943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T21:35:15.000Z","msg":"貪心的小狗最後什麼也得不到"},{"pid":"09fb77f32e74ba176fb30a8f11dc749a13e917dc","tid":308463,"uid":57168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T12:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17172594682b48fd0f8f55d237ffac06fd79c69","tid":308463,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:42:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同你差唔多 <br />\n最後揀左最愛 <br />\n<br />\n呢家後悔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇輕7年既回憶"},{"pid":"76efc9eacae8bd45f5f3c1c4448b2efdf4d6e99b","tid":308463,"uid":57168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T19:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f553648ef2a880e1a30aa54b938a9c85ceb308","tid":308463,"uid":21831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T19:27:18.000Z","msg":"我都有同樣經歷<br />\n如果你揀最愛，你注定一世比佢食住<br />\n佢到時有咩做錯唔順你意你會hurt到爆炸<br />\n但係如果揀一個佢愛你既，咁起碼佢唔會對妳唔住<br />\n而你受傷既機會亦比較低<br />\n<br />\n不過我都贊成點都比自己試一次先心息<br />\n反正都無野可以輸"},{"pid":"8a4561977aa1b44b861ab622f89cf4018b19b7ee","tid":308463,"uid":101961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T19:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主嘥氣啦 你個簡介已經係讚女神踩女友 仲話好愛佢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你只不過覺得拍咗7年就分唔化算 而且女神嗰度有咩變動又可以同番女友一齊 <br />\n加上又唔想冇咗個愛自己嘅女人咪吊住兩邊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日覺得感情事處理得唔清唔楚嘅男人唔慌好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e48010fc5d4de31e79018fd29dedddf4b9acaad","tid":308463,"uid":17881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:13:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾 冚家產啦屌你老母 死全家呀"},{"pid":"855ee2577ac8da780067fcf9e3b8e8da0685f977","tid":308463,"uid":11483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:25:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbffc46f212b9cf010b4b546b132c27ef4d98347","tid":308463,"uid":118336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:06:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"7391ad6f78f7c90303594f38a9778af5215205d3","tid":308463,"uid":31611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"我都試過咁<br />\n最後比一齊5年既女友知道左<br />\n傷盡左佢個心<br />\n雖然而家自己過得好開心<br />\n但心入面會內疚一世<br />\n覺得欠佢好多<br />\n清 做人無得貪心<br />\n同得第二個一齊其實已經簡左<br />\n要分就講得清清楚楚<br />\n唔係自己後悔"},{"pid":"1d9a658d7cfd1717eb9a67e300e9b71f41c24998","tid":308463,"uid":126376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝各位巴絲<br />\n冇錯我係垃圾係 On9仔<br />\n我以前都接受唔到任何出軌行為<br />\n但係感情事係咪可以冇時冇刻保持理性, 保持你道德標準<br />\n我相信大把人都會某程度上做錯過<br />\n但我好多謝各位屌醒我 要繼續屌亦係你地自由<br />\n特別多謝提醒我做人個位巴打<br />\n我已同女神講清楚<br />\n答返爸打問題 我冇屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢當年係錯過就係錯過左</blockquote><br />\n做乜9屈我做錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af23a0b435bbcc8663c75db79bbfa736ff305b3","tid":308463,"uid":126376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:17:54.000Z","msg":"一次過放棄曬兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}